<TEXT>
Refurbishment features strongly in a Pounds 28m batch of new contracts for
TEAM SERVICES.
The refurbishments, all in London, include the listed Royal College of
Pathologists' HQ in Carlton House Terrace (Pounds 2m), Melbourne House,
owned by Lynton, the property arm of BAA (Pounds 1.5m), Studio 6 at the BBC
