                                                            per year
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
A       up to pounds40,000      up to pounds27,000          pounds91
B         pounds40-52,000         pounds27-35,000          pounds104
C         pounds52-68,000         pounds35-45,000          pounds117
D         pounds68-88,000         pounds45-58,000          pounds130
E        pounds88-120,000         pounds58-80,000          pounds143
F        pounds120-160,000       pounds80-106,000          pounds156
